</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>小米電視整片屏幕無故掉下，中國官方已全數退款</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/31/mi-3/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=mi-3</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 31 May 2022 07:04:36 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1102415</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>日前有內地網民在微博發文，指家中的整塊小米電視螢幕自動脫落，自己掉下來摔碎，引起中國網民廣泛討論和關注。   [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>日前有內地網民在微博發文，指家中的整塊小米電視螢幕自動脫落，自己掉下來摔碎，引起中國網民廣泛討論和關注。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.27.12.jpg"> </a></p><p>中國網民「我腦公全世界最帥」日前發文，並提供一段<a href="https://weibo.com/6581354661/LvetWAZeI?pagetype=profilefeed">監控影像</a>證明，表示家中的小米電視的螢幕突然無故整塊分離。從在微博上載的照片及影片可見，電視並不是因摔落導致液晶螢幕跟白板分離，而是整片自動脫落掉下來。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.28.28.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102453" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.28.28-448x580.jpg" alt="" width="448" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.28.28-448x580.jpg 448w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.28.28-696x900.jpg 696w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.28.28-768x993.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.28.28-1187x1536.jpg 1187w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.28.28-1583x2048.jpg 1583w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.28.28.jpg 1237w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 448px" /></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1102417 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-10.18.51-694x498.png" alt="" width="694" height="498" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-10.18.51-694x498.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-10.18.51-1254x900.png 1254w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-10.18.51-768x551.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-10.18.51.png 1276w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：事主<span class="s2">微博截圖）</span></p><p>從影片可見，電視慢慢出現了一條很亮的裂縫並向下傾，事主女兒發現後嘗試把螢幕推貼回去，但最後仍是掉下來。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1102416 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-10.20.14.png" alt="" width="656" height="458" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：事主<span class="s2">微博影片截圖）</span></p><p>「我腦公全世界最帥」又指，雖然事發後第一時間向客服溝通，但對方一開始並不相信自動剝落的機會，直至提供監控影片給小米，證明螢幕分離並非人為外力造成才有後續進展。</p><p>由事主展示的淘寶訂單顯示，所購入的是小米 EA70 2022 70 吋智能電視，於去年 12 月 31 日晚間在中國小米商城發售。小米回應此屬罕見案例，目前尚未查明具體問題原因，但現時已已搬走電視，並全數退款給事主。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1102422 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-10.56.03.png" alt="" width="568" height="388" /></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.27.12.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102452" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.27.12-275x580.jpg" alt="" width="275" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.27.12-275x580.jpg 275w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.27.12-427x900.jpg 427w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.27.12-768x1619.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.27.12-728x1536.jpg 728w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-下午 1.27.12-971x2048.jpg 971w, h